VM Setup Process

0. Enable discard in VM XML file
1. Start with stock Ubuntu 16.04.x (btrfs-based install w/ compression)
2. Run all updates (sudo apt update && sudo apt full-upgrade)
3. Install dkms (from apt) + guest additions (from CD)
4. Download and manually install cu-cs-apt package
5. Install cu-cs-vm-<flavor> package via apt
6. Run update, autoremove, clean
7. Tweak Terminal Color Settings -> Tango
8. Set default launcher/desktop icons + background
9. Disable screen lock, screensaver, etc
10. Check Dropbox
11. Clear History
12. Create btrfs read-only snapshots
13. Reboot
14. Shutdown
15. Image
